statements.sql: select * from "users" where "name" = '菅原右敦' limit 1

select "users".*, "follows"."follower_id" as "pivot_follower_id", "follows"."followee_id" as "pivot_followee_id", "follows"."created_at" as "pivot_created_at", "follows"."updated_at" as "pivot_updated_at" from "users" inner join "follows" on "users"."id" = "follows"."followee_id" where "follows"."follower_id" in (3)

select "users".*, "follows"."followee_id" as "pivot_followee_id", "follows"."follower_id" as "pivot_follower_id", "follows"."created_at" as "pivot_created_at", "follows"."updated_at" as "pivot_updated_at" from "users" inner join "follows" on "users"."id" = "follows"."follower_id" where "follows"."followee_id" in (2, 4, 5)

select "users".*, "follows"."followee_id" as "pivot_followee_id", "follows"."follower_id" as "pivot_follower_id", "follows"."created_at" as "pivot_created_at", "follows"."updated_at" as "pivot_updated_at" from "users" inner join "follows" on "users"."id" = "follows"."follower_id" where "follows"."followee_id" = 3
